metadata.name: Quiver Card #1
metadata.description:
Leandro Usuna is a two-time World ISA Champion and the first Olympic surfer from Argentina. This is the first NFT in the Quiver Card Collection and captures the surf culture that Leandro is a big part of; acting as both a deeply immersed athlete and advocate of the sport in Argentina and on a global level. 
This photo was taken by photographer Pablo Franco in Argentina. 
Buyers of this NFT will be entered into a raffle for virtual meet and greets.
